name.es: SEOQuant - Cambios en métricas de GSC

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,el,en,en_AU,en_GB,e: Shows you percentage changes for clicks, impressions, CTR, and position right in Google Search Console.
short.de: Zeigt prozentuale Änderungen für Klicks, Impressionen, CTR und Position direkt in der Google Search Console an.
short.es: Muestra los cambios porcentuales de clics, impresiones, CTR y posición directamente en Google Search Console.
short.fr: Affiche les variations en pourcentage des clics, impressions, CTR et positions directement dans Google Search Console.
short.it: Mostra le variazioni percentuali di clic, impressioni, CTR e posizione direttamente in Google Search Console.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Instantly calculates and displays percentage changes for critical metrics - clicks, impressions, CTR, and position - directly within your GSC (Google Search Console) interface.

Key Features:
- Real-time Calculations: See percentage changes as you modify dates
- Seamless Integration: Works natively within the GSC dashboard
- Time-Saving: Eliminate manual calculations and spreadsheet exports
- Visual Indicators: Quickly identify positive and negative trends
- User-Friendly: Simple, clean design that doesn't clutter your workspace

SEOQuant is a tool that helps you unlock hidden Google Search Console data and access deep insights for all your sites with just a few clicks.
